## Checklist for Step 1

- [ ] Metadata name added to `ALL_METADATA_NAME` (twenty-shared)
- [ ] TypeORM entity created, extends `SyncableEntity`
- [ ] JSONB properties wrapped with `JsonbProperty<T>` (if any)
- [ ] `SerializedRelation` used for foreign keys in JSONB (if any)
- [ ] Flat entity type defined using `FlatEntityFrom<T>`
- [ ] Flat entity maps type defined
- [ ] Editable properties constant defined
- [ ] Action types defined (universal + flat)
- [ ] Registered in `AllFlatEntityTypesByMetadataName`
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_ENTITY_PROPERTIES_CONFIGURATION_BY_METADATA_NAME`
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_METADATA_RELATIONS` (for cache & transform)
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_UNIVERSAL_METADATA_RELATIONS` (for builder & runner)
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_METADATA_REQUIRED_METADATA_FOR_VALIDATION`

**TypeScript Errors?** All types should compile without errors. Fix any type issues before proceeding to Step 2.

